Elibility_criteria="""
|    | Parameter                                                                  | General Eligibility Criteria                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |\n|---:|:---------------------------------------------------------------------------|:-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\n|  0 | Bidder entity type                                                         | The Bidder shall meet the definition of a Company as defined in the RfS.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |\n|    |                                                                            |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |\n|    |                                                                            | The Bidder must not be a Limited Liability Partnership (LLP).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |\n|  1 | Restrictions on Bidders from countries that share a land border with India | In line with the O.M. issued by the Department of Expenditure, Ministry of Finance, vide No. 7/10/2021-PPD(1) dated 23.02.2023 and subsequent amendments and clarifications thereto, the Bidder shall meet the following criteria for its bid to be considered for evaluation under the RfS:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |\n|    |                                                                            |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |\n|    |                                                                            | i. Any Bidder from a country which shares a land border with India will be eligible to bid in this tender only if the bidder is registered with the Competent Authority (as defined in the OM as referred above).                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |\n|    |                                                                            |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |\n|    |                                                                            | ii. Any Bidder (including an Indian Bidder) who has a Specified Transfer of Technology (ToT) arrangement with an entity from a country which shares a land border with India will be eligible to participate in this RfS only if the Bidder is registered with the Competent Authority under the referred OM.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |\n|    |                                                                            |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |\n|    |                                                                            | iii. “Bidder” in this reference, means any person or firm or company, including any member of a consortium, every artificial juridical person not falling in any of the descriptions of bidders stated hereinbefore, including any agency branch or office controlled by such person, participating in this tender.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |\n|    |                                                                            |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |\n|    |                                                                            | iv. “Bidder from a country which shares a land border with India” for the purpose of this clause, means:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |\n|    |                                                                            | i. An entity incorporated, established or registered in such a country; or                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |\n|    |                                                                            | ii. A subsidiary of an entity incorporated, established or registered in such a country; or                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |\n|    |                                                                            | iii. An entity substantially controlled through entities incorporated, established or registered in such a country; or                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |\n|    |                                                                            | iv. An entity whose beneficial owner is situated in such a country; or                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |\n|    |                                                                            | v. An Indian (or other) agent of such an entity; or                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |\n|    |                                                                            | vi. A natural person who is a citizen of such a country; or                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |\n|    |                                                                            | vii. A consortium where any member of the consortium falls under any of the above.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           |\n|    |                                                                            |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |\n|    |                                                                            | v. “Beneficial owner” for the purposes of Clause 36.4.iv.iv. above will be as defined in the referred OM, including subsequent amendments and clarifications thereto.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |\n|    |                                                                            |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |\n|    |                                                                            | vi. In support of the above, the Bidder shall be required to submit necessary Undertaking, as per Format 7.8/7.8A of the RfS.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |\n|  2 | nan                                                                        | As on the bid submission deadline, Bidder or any of its Affiliates should not be a willful defaulter to any lender. Further, as on the bid submission deadline, the Bidder & any of its Affiliate including any Consortium Member & any of its Affiliate, their directors should not have been debarred or included in the blacklist by any government agency or authority in India, the government of the jurisdiction of the Bidder or Members where they are incorporated or the jurisdiction of their principal place of business, any international financial institution such as the World Bank Group, Asian Development Bank, African Development Bank, Inter-American Development Bank, Asian Infrastructure Investment Bank, etc. or the United Nations or any of its agencies. The Bidder shall submit an undertaking to this effect as per Format 7.7 of the RfS. |\n|  3 | 2                                                                          | Technical Eligibility Criteria                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |\n|  4 | Use of suitable equipment                                                  | The Bidder deploys type certified wind turbine models listed in Revised List of Models and Manufactures (RLMM) issued by MNRE as updated until the SCSD of the Project.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |\n|    |                                                                            |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |\n|    |                                                                            | The modules used in the Projects under this RfS should have been included in the List-I under the “Approved Models and Manufacturers of Solar Photovoltaic Modules (Requirement of Compulsory Registration) Order, 2019-Implementation-Reg.”, as on the date of invoicing of such modules.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |\n|  5 | Compliance with technical standards and guidelines                         | The projects should comply with the criteria for power supply as detailed in Clause 8 of the RfS, be developed as per the Guidelines issued by the Government of India from time to time, and be governed by the applicable technical standards issued by the Government from time to time.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |\n|  6 | 3                                                                          | Financial Eligibility Criteria                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |\n|  7 | Net-Worth Criteria                                                         | The Bidder\'s Net-Worth should be equal to or greater than the amount calculated as 10 times the amount payable as part of EMD in line with Clause 17 of the RfS. The  Net-Worth amount should be demonstrated by the Bidder as on the last of previous Financial Year, or as on the day at least 7 days prior to the bid submission deadline.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |\n|  8 | Liquidity Criteria                                                         | The Bidder must demonstrate atleast one of the following parameters to ascertain that the Bidder has sufficient means to manage the fund requirements for the Project:                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |\n|    |                                                                            |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |\n|    |                                                                            | 1) A minimum annual turnover (excluding "Other Income" as indicated in the annual accounts of the Bidder) of INR 2,00,94,000/MW (Indian Rupees Two Crore and Ninety-Four Thousand/MW) of the quoted Contracted Capacity during the previous financial year or as on the day at least 7 days prior to the bid submission deadline.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |\n|    |                                                                            |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |\n|    |                                                                            | 2) Internal resource generation capability, in the form of Profit Before Depreciation Interest and Taxes (PBDIT) excluding other and exceptional income for a minimum amount of INR 40,18,800/MW (Indian Rupees Forty Lakhs Eighteen Thousand and Eight Hundred/MW) of the quoted capacity, as on the last date of previous financial year or as on the day at least 7 days prior to the bid submission deadline.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |\n|    |                                                                            |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |\n|    |                                                                            | 3) In-principle sanction letter from the lending institutions/ banks of the Bidder, committing a Line of Credit for a minimum amount of INR 50,23,500/MW (Indian Rupees Fifty Lakhs Twenty-three Thousand and Five Hundred/MW) of the quoted capacity, towards meeting the working capital requirement of the project quoted under this RfS.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
"""
tendersummary="The first 10 pages of the document provide a range of information regarding the regulations, fees, bidding process, contact details, and interpretation of terms. The document starts with a table listing various regulations, sections, and subsections mentioned throughout the document. It then provides a context and summary of the tender document, including the title, purpose, and issuing authority. The document also includes a disclaimer, stating that SECI reserves the right to modify the document and that it is prepared in good faith.\n\nThe pages also outline the bidding process and fees associated with the Request for Selection (RfS) for the supply of 1000 MW of firm and dispatchable power. It mentions a document fee, bid processing fee, earnest money deposit, and performance bank guarantee. The page provides the date, time, and venue of the pre-bid meeting, as well as the deadlines for bid submission and the e-Reverse Auction (e-RA).\n\nContact information for SECI and ISN-ETS is provided for any assistance required. Bidders are reminded to comply with the RfS documents and can download the complete document from the ISN-ETS Portal or SECI website. Clarifications and amendments will also be available on these websites.\n\nThe document then explains the objective of the bidding process, which is to provide firm and dispatchable renewable energy power to Distribution Companies (DISCOMs) through renewable energy sources. It highlights SECI's role in the implementation of the National Solar Mission and the government's efforts to reduce risks and bring down tariffs in the solar and wind power sector. The guidelines for the tariff-based competitive bidding process are also outlined.\n\nThe process of selecting successful bidders is discussed, indicating that power will be sold to the Punjab State Power Corporation Limited (PSPCL) on a back-to-back basis. Bidders are encouraged to avail fiscal incentives for their renewable energy projects, and those who have already commissioned or are constructing projects may be given a longer period of Power Purchase Agreement (PPA). The bidding procedure is explained as a Single Stage, Two-Envelope Bidding Procedure, and interested bidders must register on the ISN-ETS portal.\n\nThe document also provides instructions for obtaining further information and emphasizes the importance of properly uploading bids on the Electronic Tendering System (ETS) portal. It states that RfS documents can be downloaded from the ETS portal or SECI's website and that any amendments or clarifications will be uploaded on the ETS website. SECI reserves the right to cancel or withdraw the invitation for bids without providing a reason.\n\nLastly, the document includes interpretations of terms and phrases used in the agreement. It clarifies the meaning of singular and plural forms, applicable laws, time of day, interpretation of different parts of the contract, and the purpose of the table of contents and headings.\n\nOverall, the first 10 pages of the document provide comprehensive information about the regulations, fees, bidding process, and contact details for the Request for Selection (RfS) for the supply of 1000 MW of firm and dispatchable power from ISTS-connected renewable energy projects in India."

